Jared給我看了那人的照片
Jared showed me the photos of the men

865
00:51:44,998 --> 00:51:46,965
在燒烤時候看我們的那個人
who were watching us at the barbecue.

866
00:51:46,967 --> 00:51:48,800
他們在拍我們, Matt! 好
They're filming us, Matt! Okay.

867
00:51:48,802 --> 00:51:51,169
你把這些帶到醫院來幹啥?
Why are you bringing this up at the hospital?

868
00:51:51,171 --> 00:51:52,737
放鬆!
Relax!

