I think if we never say the word "America."

909
00:54:47,013 --> 00:54:48,546
是, 我們只是拿一個美國符號
Oh, yeah, we just take an American symbol.

910
00:54:48,548 --> 00:54:50,081
就是. 老鷹
Exactly. Eagle.

911
00:54:50,083 --> 00:54:51,149
- 自由. - 前沿
- Freedom. - Frontier.

912
00:54:51,151 --> 00:54:53,284
前沿
Frontier.

913
00:54:53,286 --> 00:54:56,387
那個需要在那邊做個坑
So that needs to make that pothole there.

914
00:54:56,389 --> 00:54:57,922
那個上面有沒有標籤?
Does that have a label on it?

915
00:54:57,924 --> 00:55:01,226
B. 那它就剛好在你腳那. 完美
B. So that goes right at your feet. Perfect.

916
00:55:01,228 --> 00:55:03,228
我剛想出個點子
I just got an idea.

917
00:55:03,230 --> 00:55:04,863
你覺得他們上到去後我們該讓他們做什麼?
You know what we've gotta have them do when they're up there?

918
00:55:04,865 --> 00:55:06,397
是誰, 伽利略還是誰, 說過...
Who is it, Galileo or somebody, said...

919
00:55:06,399 --> 00:55:07,599
扔羽毛
Oh, drop the feather.

