00:55:10,437 --> 00:55:12,637
鎯頭和羽毛會以相同速度落下
a hammer and a feather would fall at the same speed.

923
00:55:12,639 --> 00:55:14,405
嗯, 好, 但我們該怎麼做出這效果?
Well, okay, but how are we gonna do that?

924
00:55:14,407 --> 00:55:16,341
用鉛做的羽毛
A lead feather.

925
00:55:16,343 --> 00:55:19,277
等等, 我們必須讓旗幟盡可能的穩定
Wait a minute, we gotta keep the flag as stable as possible,

926
00:55:19,279 --> 00:55:21,913
因為旗子飄說明有風
because the wind resistance makes it billow.

927
00:55:21,915 --> 00:55:23,548
你揮旗. 你不能揮!
You wave the flag. You can't do that!

928
00:55:23,550 --> 00:55:25,516
好休斯頓, 我準備走出登月艙
Okay Houston, I'm about to step off the LM.

929
00:55:25,518 --> 00:55:27,886
他在那留下了個腳印
He leaves a footprint there.

930
00:55:27,888 --> 00:55:29,487
因為他們會在那留下腳印. 就是!
'Cause they would leave footprints there. Exactly!

931
00:55:29,489 --> 00:55:31,890
我們可以把那些照片傳送回家
And we so can send photographs of that back home.

932
00:55:31,892 --> 00:55:34,325
它是...那是...就是那個畫面!
It's... that's...That is the image!

933
00:55:34,327 --> 00:55:35,560
寫下來! 腳印!
Write that down, the footprints!

