it looks like a towering leap.

949
00:56:14,534 --> 00:56:16,601
像是躍進. 像是跳躍
It's like a leap. It's like a jump.

950
00:56:16,603 --> 00:56:19,237
這個躍進是為了...為了一切!
And this is a leap forward for...For everything!

951
00:56:19,239 --> 00:56:20,571
