Did you say hi? Did he look at you when you came in?

963
00:57:02,716 --> 00:57:04,282
裏頭究竟有人沒人?
Is there even a guy in there?

964
00:57:04,284 --> 00:57:06,050
他一直坐在那看
He's sitting there watching.

965
00:57:06,052 --> 00:57:08,019
