以便測試登陸模塊
to test out the landing module,

1010
00:59:13,746 --> 00:59:17,348
然後直到載人登月
and, uh, then move on towards landing a man on the moon

1011
00:59:17,350 --> 00:59:20,351
七月中旬還有兩次飛行
two flights further on in the middle of July.

1012
00:59:22,287 --> 00:59:26,257
我們有一個消息和一個壞消息
So we've got good news and bad news.

1013
00:59:26,259 --> 00:59:30,795
好消息, 他的名字叫Antonin Lhotsky
Good news, his name is Antonin Lhotsky.

1014
00:59:30,797 --> 00:59:33,464
嗯. - 他是名克格勃特工
Uh-huh. - He's a KGB agent.

1015
00:59:33,466 --> 00:59:35,433
他就是那天晚上在工作室外頭那人
He's the man from outside the studio the other night.

1016
00:59:35,435 --> 00:59:37,301
哇, 什麼?
Whoa, what?

1017
00:59:37,303 --> 00:59:39,570
我們懷疑他一直就是那個鼴鼠
We suspect he's been the mole the entire time.

1018
00:59:39,572 --> 00:59:42,473
所以...所以他知道雪崩行動. 我們完蛋了!
So... so then he knows about avalanche. We're fucked!

1019
00:59:42,475 --> 00:59:44,408
我們覺得他並不知道
We don't think he does.

1020
00:59:44,410 --> 00:59:46,177
這幾天我們一直在審問他
We've been interrogating him for the past couple of days.

1021
00:59:46,179 --> 00:59:47,378
看起來他什麼都不知道
He doesn't seem to know anything.

1022
00:59:47,380 --> 00:59:49,814
我們突擊搜查了他的房子. 啥都沒有
We've raided his house. Nothing.

1023
00:59:49,816 --> 00:59:52,483
這人就是鼴鼠? 你們...你們抓到他了?
This guy's the mole? And you... you got him?

1024
00:59:52,485 --> 00:59:53,918
我們抓到他了
We got him.

1025
00:59:54,853 --> 00:59:59,657
然後怎麼? 我們才剛剛...
So, then what? We're just...

1026
00:59:59,659 --> 01:00:00,758
那我們沒事?
We're good?

1027
01:00:00,760 --> 01:00:02,627
嗯, 有一點
Well, not entirely.

1028
01:00:02,629 --> 01:00:06,531
我們, 額, 收到了新的情報, 蘇聯方面的進展
We, uh, got some new intel on the Soviet progress,

1029
01:00:06,533 --> 01:00:09,700
說明他們做得比我們原想的要好
and it turns out they're doing better than we thought.

1030
01:00:09,702 --> 01:00:14,805
看起來他們有可能在'69年底登月
It looks like they could possibly make it to the moon by the end of '69.

1031
01:00:14,807 --> 01:00:19,177
意味著我們最晚在四月份要全部做完
Which means that we need to be done by April at the latest.

1032
01:00:20,546 --> 01:00:23,581
這讓我們的時間非常緊迫
Yeah, that puts us on a pretty tight timeline.

1033
01:00:23,583 --> 01:00:25,416
他們知道我們在這
They know we're here.

1034
01:00:25,418 --> 01:00:27,318
我們可以在這, 好吧? 放鬆
We're allowed to be here, okay? Relax.

1035
01:00:27,320 --> 01:00:28,953
嗨
Hi.

1036
01:00:34,560 --> 01:00:36,761
追, 追, 追, 追!
Go, go, go, go!

1037
01:00:38,564 --> 01:00:40,731
Jared, 上車!
Jared, get in the car!

1038
01:01:07,359 --> 01:01:09,427
喂? Matt, 我們碰到麻煩了
Hello? Matt, we have a problem here.

1039
01:01:12,232 --> 01:01:16,601
有合同的人, 我不知道, 有的人
Gentleman got the contract with, I don't know, somebody.

1040
01:01:16,603 --> 01:01:18,936
這是他們說是鼴鼠的那個人
This is who they say the mole was.

1041
01:01:18,938 --> 01:01:21,505
我們採訪過他?
So we interviewed him?

1042
01:01:21,507 --> 01:01:24,942
是, 一年多前
Yeah, over a year ago.

1043
01:01:24,944 --> 01:01:28,012
記不記得你曾經讓我查過是誰給Webb打的電話?
Remember when you asked me to find out who was on the phone with Webb?

1044
01:01:28,014 --> 01:01:29,413
當然
Of course.

1045
01:01:29,415 --> 01:01:31,549
我記得
I did.

1046
01:01:31,551 --> 01:01:33,517
...秒降到月球表面
...second burn to the lunar surface.

1047
01:01:33,519 --> 01:01:35,786
然後我們可以進去...250
Then we can go in after...For 250.

1048
01:01:35,788 --> 01:01:38,256
我們只能做到250秒?
250 seconds is all we can do?

1049
01:01:38,258 --> 01:01:40,591
那是最大值. 你知不知道...
That's the maximum, and you know that...

1050
01:01:40,593 --> 01:01:42,627
你有沒和TRW討論過?
Did you talk to TRW?

1051
01:01:42,629 --> 01:01:45,796
是. 你知道他們的燃料的情況
Yeah. And you know how they are about their fuels.

1052
01:01:45,798 --> 01:01:47,531
所以我們有麻煩了...Grumman...
So we are in trouble...Grumman...

1053
01:01:49,302 --> 01:01:50,668
這什麼意思?
What does this mean?

1054
01:01:52,738 --> 01:01:57,008
所以鼴鼠知道我們登不了月
So the mole knew that we couldn't make it to the moon

1055
01:01:57,010 --> 01:02:00,344
一年多了?
for over a year?

1056
01:02:00,346 --> 01:02:02,647
我覺得不是
I don't think so.

1057
01:02:02,649 --> 01:02:04,715
我覺得Lhotsky不是那個鼴鼠
I don't think that Lhotsky's the mole,

1058
01:02:04,717 --> 01:02:08,419
我覺得工作室外頭那人不是Lhotsky
I don't think Lhotsky was outside the studio.

1059
01:02:08,421 --> 01:02:10,621
我的意思是, Lhotsky知道我們登不了月
I mean, Lhotsky knows that we can't make it to the moon,

1060
01:02:10,623 --> 01:02:12,023
所以也許他們...他不配合
so maybe they...He wouldn't cooperate

1061
01:02:12,025 --> 01:02:14,325
然後他們只好把他弄成替罪羊
and they had to make him a fall guy

1062
01:02:14,327 --> 01:02:15,426
說他就是那個鼴鼠
by saying that he's the mole.

1063
01:02:15,428 --> 01:02:16,494
他們?
They?

1064
01:02:17,663 --> 01:02:18,929
對
Yeah.

1065
01:02:18,931 --> 01:02:21,866
什麼意思? 中情局
What do you mean? The CIA.

1066
01:02:21,868 --> 01:02:25,736
好, 那麼, 在工作室外頭跟蹤我們的人是誰?
Okay, well then, who's outside the studio following us?

1067
01:02:25,738 --> 01:02:27,672
CIA特工
CIA agents.

1068
01:02:27,674 --> 01:02:30,641
所以boles沒對他們開槍
That's why boles didn't shoot them.

1069
01:02:30,643 --> 01:02:32,310
他們是一夥的
They're all working together.

1070
01:02:32,312 --> 01:02:34,779
他們全都在監視我們, 他們騙我們
They're all watching us, and they're lying to us.

1071
01:02:34,781 --> 01:02:36,347
為什麼? 有什麼目的?
For what? For what purpose?

1072
01:02:36,349 --> 01:02:37,615
我們做的一切他們全都知道
They know everything that we're doing.

1073
01:02:37,617 --> 01:02:39,884
為什麼...完全沒道理
Why... This doesn't make any sense.

1074
01:02:39,886 --> 01:02:42,820
他們沒理由跟蹤我們
There's no reason for them to be following us.

1075
01:02:42,822 --> 01:02:44,555
你...你有沒有...
You... have you...

1076
01:02:44,557 --> 01:02:47,525
以前你有沒有聽過陰謀論?
Have you heard of a conspiracy theory before?

1077
01:02:47,527 --> 01:02:49,527
有
Yeah.

1078
01:02:49,529 --> 01:02:51,395
我覺得我們現在就在裏頭
I think we're in one.

1079
01:03:52,124 --> 01:03:54,058
好, 伸腿!
Okay, leg out!

1080
01:03:55,428 --> 01:03:56,660
看起來不夠真實
That doesn't look real.

1081
01:03:56,662 --> 01:03:58,028
好, 知道我們該怎麼做嗎?
Okay, you know what we'll do?

1082
01:03:58,030 --> 01:04:00,731
數三下跳下來. 準備好了?
Jump on the count of three. Ready?

1083
01:04:00,733 --> 01:04:01,966
我會帶來反彈
I'm bringing the bounce in.

1084
01:04:01,968 --> 01:04:03,834
太高了
That's a big jump.

1085
01:04:03,836 --> 01:04:05,436
快, 你是Neil Armstrong
Come on, you're supposed to be Neil Armstrong.

1086
01:04:05,438 --> 01:04:06,570
他很勇敢. 準備好了?
He's brave. Ready?

1087
01:04:06,572 --> 01:04:08,506
開始
There we go.

1088
01:04:11,176 --> 01:04:13,511
額, 換個背景
Uh, change the background.

1089
01:04:17,082 --> 01:04:18,849
再換一個
One more.

1090
01:04:20,919 --> 01:04:21,986
這個怎麼樣?
How about that?

1091
01:04:21,988 --> 01:04:23,888
棒
Great.

1092
01:04:23,890 --> 01:04:25,990
很棒
That's great.

1093
01:04:25,992 --> 01:04:27,792
我們在他頭盔的反射裏頭拍到了啥?
What are we getting in the reflection of his helmet?

1094
01:04:27,794 --> 01:04:29,160
我在不在裏面?
Am I in it?

1095
01:04:29,162 --> 01:04:30,628
我們必須在後面替換掉
We'll have to replace that after.

1096
01:04:42,707 --> 01:04:44,708
看起來很棒. 你只要...
That looks great. And then you just...

1097
01:04:44,710 --> 01:04:46,477
我們必須按住這
We have to repress this.

1098
01:04:46,479 --> 01:04:47,845
放到動畫板上重拍
Put that on an animation stand and reshoot it.

1099
01:04:47,847 --> 01:04:50,514
這個是原版
This is the original from the sound stage.

1100
01:04:50,516 --> 01:04:52,550
然後加上環形山的紋理
And the crater textures are added after.

1101
01:04:52,552 --> 01:04:54,852
在工作室裏去除掉細節
Getting rid of the details in the studio.

1102
01:04:54,854 --> 01:04:57,588
你進去然後你用印刷油墨把這些區域塗黑
You go in and you black out the areas with litho ink.

1103
01:04:57,590 --> 01:05:00,191
讓我們把這個移下一點
Let's move this a little bit further down,

1104
01:05:00,193 --> 01:05:02,893
因為看起來有點太過直角了
because it seems a little too square.

1105
01:05:02,895 --> 01:05:04,495
和鏡頭成直角? 是
Square to camera? Yeah.

1106
01:05:04,497 --> 01:05:05,563
好
Sure.

1107
01:05:10,735 --> 01:05:12,169
哇
Wow.

1108
01:05:24,883 --> 01:05:28,152
好了? 很好. 好, 開始
Ready? That's good. Yeah, go.

1109
01:05:28,154 --> 01:05:30,621
成功了
It works.

1110
01:05:30,623 --> 01:05:31,922
Yes!
Yes!

1111
01:05:34,092 --> 01:05:35,192
太神奇了! 再來一遍
This is amazing! Go again.

1112
01:05:35,194 --> 01:05:37,828
Matt. 嗯?
Matt. Yes?

1113
01:05:37,830 --> 01:05:39,230
看到這個沒有? 看到這個沒有?
Have you seen this? Have you seen this?

1114
01:05:39,232 --> 01:05:42,500
再來一遍! 再來一遍! Owen, 看, 看
Do it again! Do it again! Owen, look, look.

1115
01:05:42,502 --> 01:05:44,268
鎯頭, 羽毛
Hammer, feather.

1116
01:05:44,270 --> 01:05:46,537
落! 伽利略是對的
Drop! Galileo was right.

1117
01:05:46,539 --> 01:05:49,874
帥哥, 我在裏頭加在重量. 什麼?
Dude, I just put a weight in it. What?

1118
01:05:49,876 --> 01:05:52,643
"NASA科學家死了"
"NASA scientist dies."

1119
01:05:52,645 --> 01:05:54,144
今天早上的報紙
It's from this morning's paper.

1120
01:05:56,548 --> 01:05:59,550
搞啥...Matt, 是Lhotsky
Well, what the...Matt, it's Lhotsky.

1121
01:05:59,552 --> 01:06:00,784
什麼?
What?

1122
01:06:00,786 --> 01:06:02,953
Boles, 他肯定知道
Boles, he must've known about it.

1123
01:06:04,189 --> 01:06:05,990
聽著, 想想Lhotsky為什麼會死
Listen, think why Lhotsky's dead.

1124
01:06:05,992 --> 01:06:07,858
顯然, 是他在和Webb說話, 所以他們啥了他
Obviously, he was talking to Webb, so they killed him.

1125
01:06:07,860 --> 01:06:09,860
他們會殺了我...
They're going to kill me...

1126
01:06:09,862 --> 01:06:11,896
我們不知道那人為什麼死了. 不, 我們知道
We don't know why that guy's dead. Yes, we do.

1127
01:06:11,898 --> 01:06:14,031
他們會啥了我? 你在說什麼?
They're going to kill me? What are you talking about?

1128
01:06:14,033 --> 01:06:15,699
他們會把我們都殺了. 他們會殺了宇航員
They're going to kill us both, they're going to kill the astronauts.

1129
01:06:15,701 --> 01:06:17,935
我肯定...任何知道這事的人
I'm sure... Anyone who knows about this.

1130
01:06:17,937 --> 01:06:20,304
我肯定Lhotsky知道得太多了所以他們把他幹掉了. 就是這樣
I'm sure Lhotsky knew too much and so they got rid of him. Okay? That's it.

1131
01:06:20,306 --> 01:06:22,940
對! 對! 我說的就是這個!
Right! Right! That's what I'm talking about!

1132
01:06:22,942 --> 01:06:25,576
他就是那個鼴鼠, 好嗎?
He was the mole, okay?

1133
01:06:25,578 --> 01:06:28,612
不...他們在把東西串起來
No... no, they're tying off loose ends!

1134
01:06:28,614 --> 01:06:30,614
好, 那其他還有誰會死, 啊?
Yeah, and, so, who else is gonna die, huh?

1135
01:06:30,616 --> 01:06:33,551
他們會殺了Jim Webb? NASA的頭? 他也知道!
They're gonna kill Jim Webb? The head of NASA? He knows, too!

1136
01:06:33,553 --> 01:06:35,819
有可能. 有可能. 你不覺得他們會?
Maybe. Maybe. You don't think they would?

1137
01:06:35,821 --> 01:06:39,790
不! 好了, 穿上宇航服準備好, 行嗎? 閉嘴吧你
No! Okay, put the suit on and get ready, all right? Shut the fuck up.

1138
01:06:54,974 --> 01:06:59,577
有團東西在...在玻璃上. Owen, 你能擦掉嗎?
There's a glob of something on the...on the glass. Owen, could you get it?

1139
01:06:59,579 --> 01:07:02,646
不, 就在...你沒擦掉. 就在那兒
No, it's right... You didn't get it. It's right there.

1140
01:07:02,648 --> 01:07:05,249
就在, 就在那
Right, right there.

1141
01:07:05,251 --> 01:07:07,918
你...你在做什麼? 這只是個測試
What... What are you doing? It's just a test.

1142
01:07:07,920 --> 01:07:09,954
Boles, 我不接受你的命令!
Boles, I don't take orders from you!

1143
01:07:09,956 --> 01:07:12,122
- 哦, 真的? - 好了, 過來
- Oh, really? - Enough, come on.

1144
01:07:12,124 --> 01:07:14,758
是, 有人會讓我們被殺掉. 我不要接受他的命令
Yeah, I don't take orders from someone who's trying to get us killed.

1145
01:07:14,760 --> 01:07:16,627
Owen, Owen, Owen. 另扔了
Owen, Owen, Owen. Don't drop it.

1146
01:07:16,629 --> 01:07:17,861
他放他們走的. 不, 他沒有...
He let them get away. No, he didn't...

1147
01:07:17,863 --> 01:07:19,363
對不對? 他放他們走的!
Right? He let them get away!

1148
01:07:19,365 --> 01:07:21,165
你就是那麼做的. 哦, 真的?
That's what you did. Oh, really?

1149
01:07:21,167 --> 01:07:23,200
- 對, 你故意錯過的! - 嗨, 哇, 哇, 哇!
- Yes, you missed on purpose! - Hey, whoa, whoa, whoa!

1150
01:07:23,202 --> 01:07:25,769
你...你在幹什麼? 你在幹什麼? 我們是朋友
What... what are you doing? What are you doing? We're friends.

1151
01:07:25,771 --> 01:07:27,304
他們是誰? 我們是朋友
Who are they? We're friends.

1152
01:07:27,306 --> 01:07:30,341
他們是誰? 是不是Brackett? 中情局?
Who are they? Is it Brackett? The CIA?

1153
01:07:30,343 --> 01:07:32,810
為什麼你不告訴他你每天都怎麼在一直給Barckett打電話
Why don't you tell him about how you've been calling Brackett every day,

1154
01:07:32,812 --> 01:07:36,647
想讓Johnson總統扔掉這個任務. 告訴他!
trying to get Johnson thrown off the mission. Tell him that!

1155
01:07:36,649 --> 01:07:38,916
你在說什麼? 嗨, 問你的朋友
What are you talking about? Hey, ask your friend.

1156
01:07:44,255 --> 01:07:45,623
好, 等等
Okay, hold on.

1157
01:07:45,625 --> 01:07:48,192
告訴他. 告訴他
Tell him. Tell him.

1158
01:08:06,211 --> 01:08:08,812
我們決定登月
We choose to go to the moon.

1159
01:08:08,814 --> 01:08:10,781
我們決定登月
We choose to go to the moon.

1160
01:08:17,188 --> 01:08:19,757
我們決定在這個年代登月
We choose to go to the moon in this decade

1161
01:08:19,759 --> 01:08:21,759
以及成就其他
and do the other things.

1162
01:08:21,761 --> 01:08:25,262
不是因為它們輕而易舉，而是因為它們困難重重
Not because they are easy, but because they are hard.

1163
01:08:25,264 --> 01:08:29,333
因為這個目標能夠組織和檢驗
Because that goal will serve to organize and measure

1164
01:08:29,335 --> 01:08:33,037
我們最強的能量和技術
the best of our energies and skills.

1165
01:08:33,039 --> 01:08:36,840
因為這項挑戰我們願意接受
Because that challenge is one that we're willing to accept.

1166
01:08:36,842 --> 01:08:42,713
我們不願推後, 我們決戰決勝, 其他也是一樣
One we are unwilling to postpone, and one we intend to win, and the others, too.

1167
01:08:49,921 --> 01:08:52,089
我們將把火箭發射到
We shall send to the moon,

1168
01:08:52,091 --> 01:08:57,861
和休斯頓控制室相距38萬公里的月球上
240,000 miles away from the control station in Houston,

1169
01:08:57,863 --> 01:09:00,030
一枚巨型火箭
a giant rocket,

1170
01:09:00,032 --> 01:09:04,702
高度將近100米, 相當於這個橄欖球場的長度
more than 300 feet tall, the length of this football field,

1171
01:09:04,704 --> 01:09:09,473
採用新合金來製造, 其中有些還沒被開發出來
made of new metal alloys, some of which have not yet been invented,

